data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom home. The main level offers the kitchen with wood floors & oak cabinets, dining room, living room with built ins around the large window, family room with gas fireplace, half bath & laundry. The upper level offers 3 nice bedrooms & a full bath. The mostly finished lower level has a family room & game room. Other features include a front porch & rear deck, double attached garage, freshly painted exterior in 2021 & a fenced in backyard! Great East side location that is close to Bertha Godfrey school.
